snippet.title: 2021: A Crazy Year In America | The Amber Ruffin Show
snippet.description:
The Amber Ruffin Show. New Episodes Streaming Every Friday on Peacock: https://pck.tv/3pOiao8

Reserve your spot in the live studio audience for The Amber Ruffin Show at https://1iota.com/show/1210/the-amber-ruffin-show

It has been a crazy year in America, let's find out what happened! From the Olympics to a new President to COVID vaccines, 2021 was a year of growth, rebirth, and change, and here at The Amber Ruffin Show, we are so thankful to have gotten to share it with you. Check out Amber's best headlines of 2021 now!

 #TheAmberRuffinShow #PeacockTV #YearReview

Show Synopsis: Amber showcases her signature smart-and-silly take on the news of the week, responding to it all with a charming, late-night mix of seriousness, nonsense, and evening gowns.

About Peacock: The streaming service from NBCUniversal that’s as free as a bird. Current hits. Timeless classics. Timely updates. Stream Now With Peacock, stream current hits, hundreds of movies, thousands of episodes of TV shows, and exclusive Originals – plus timely news, live sports, WWE, and daily pop culture. Peacock’s got all your faves, including Parks & Rec, Yellowstone, Modern Family, and every episode of The Office.
